      • getDefaultTracker

        public static Tracker getDefaultTracker()
        Returns:
        the default Tracker, or null if no default is set

      • setDefaultTracker

        public static void setDefaultTracker(Tracker tracker)
        Set a specific Tracker instance as the default tracker. The Tracker will be added to the Snowplow class if its namespace is not already stored. The first Tracker created using createTracker() or registered with registerTracker() will automatically be the default tracker; this method is intended for use with multiple trackers.
        Parameters:
        tracker - the tracker to use as default

      • setDefaultTracker

        public static boolean setDefaultTracker(java.lang.String namespace)
        Set a registered Tracker as the default tracker, using its namespace.
        Parameters:
        namespace - the namespace of the tracker to set as default
        Returns:
        true if the tracker was found and set
